                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <CheckCircle2 className="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Total maturity value of your SIP investment</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <CheckCircle2 className="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Inflation-adjusted real returns (when enabled)</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <CheckCircle2 className="w-5 h-5 text-teal-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Year-by-year growth projection</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </CardContent>
            </Card>

            {/* What This Calculator Does NOT Do */}
            <Card className="border-0 shadow-lg rounded-2xl bg-amber-50">
                <CardHeader>
                    <CardTitle className="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-3">
                        <AlertCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-amber-600" />
                        What This Calculator Does NOT Do
                    </CardTitle>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                    <div className="space-y-4">
                        <p className="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
                            It's important to understand the limitations of this calculator:
                        </p>
                        <ul className="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <AlertCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Does not account for actual market volatility or fund-specific performance variations</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <AlertCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Does not consider expense ratios, exit loads, or fund management fees</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <AlertCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Does not account for tax implications on returns (LTCG, STCG taxes)</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <AlertCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Does not guarantee actual returns - results are mathematical estimates only</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <AlertCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Does not account for fund-specific risks, management changes, or scheme modifications</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <AlertCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Does not consider market timing, investment date variations, or NAV fluctuations</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <AlertCircle className="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span>Does not provide investment recommendations or financial advice</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </CardContent>
            </Card>

            {/* Assumptions */}
            <Card className="border-0 shadow-lg rounded-2xl bg-blue-50">
                <CardHeader>
                    <CardTitle className="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Info className="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" />
                        Calculator Assumptions
                    </CardTitle>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                    <div className="space-y-4">
                        <p className="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
                            This calculator uses the following assumptions in its calculations:
                        </p>
                        <ul className="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <Info className="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span><strong>Constant Return Rate:</strong> Assumes the expected return rate remains constant throughout the investment period. In reality, returns vary monthly based on market conditions, fund performance, and economic factors.</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <Info className="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span><strong>Investment Timing:</strong> Assumes investments are made at the beginning of each month, with immediate compounding from the first month.</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <Info className="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span><strong>No Interruptions:</strong> Assumes no withdrawals, pauses, or changes to the SIP amount during the investment period.</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <Info className="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span><strong>Constant Inflation:</strong> When inflation adjustment is enabled, assumes the inflation rate remains constant throughout the period.</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <Info className="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span><strong>No Charges:</strong> Does not account for expense ratios, entry/exit loads, transaction charges, or fund management fees.</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <Info className="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span><strong>No Taxes:</strong> Calculations do not consider tax implications such as Long-Term Capital Gains (LTCG) or Short-Term Capital Gains (STCG) taxes.</span>
                            </li>
                            <li className="flex items-start gap-2">
                                <Info className="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                                <span><strong>Formula Basis:</strong> Uses the standard future value of annuity formula: FV = P × [((1 + r)^n - 1) / r] × (1 + r)</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </CardContent>
            </Card>

            {/* Example Calculation */}
            <Card className="border-0 shadow-lg rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white">
                <CardHeader>
                    <CardTitle className="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-3">
                        <Calculator className="w-6 h-6 text-teal-600" />
                        Example Calculation
                    </CardTitle>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                    <div className="space-y-4">
                        <p className="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
                            Here's a detailed example to help you understand how the SIP calculator works:
                        </p>
                        <div className="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-6 font-mono">
                            <div className="space-y-3">
                                <div>
                                    <span className="text-slate-400">Monthly SIP Amount:</span> <span className="text-white font-bold">₹10,000</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <span className="text-slate-400">Investment Period:</span> <span className="text-white font-bold">20 years (240 months)</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <span className="text-slate-400">Expected Return:</span> <span className="text-white font-bold">12% p.a. (1% monthly)</span>
                                </div>
                                <div className="pt-3 border-t border-slate-700">
                                    <div className="text-emerald-400 font-semibold mb-2">Calculation:</div>
                                    <div className="text-sm space-y-1 text-slate-300">
                                        <div>FV = ₹10,000 × [((1.01)^240 - 1) / 0.01] × 1.01</div>
                                        <div>FV = ₹10,000 × [10.89 - 1] / 0.01 × 1.01</div>
                                        <div>FV = ₹10,000 × 989 × 1.01</div>
                                        <div className="text-emerald-400 font-bold text-lg mt-2">FV ≈ ₹99.91 Lakhs</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div className="pt-3 border-t border-slate-700">
                                    <div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
                                        <div>
                                            <span className="text-slate-400">Total Invested:</span> <span className="text-white font-bold">₹24 Lakhs</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <span className="text-slate-400">Estimated Returns:</span> <span className="text-emerald-400 font-bold">₹75.91 Lakhs</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p className="text-sm text-slate-600 italic">
                            Note: This is an example calculation. Actual returns will vary based on real market conditions and fund performance.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </CardContent>
            </Card>

            {/* Introduction */}
            <Card className="border-0 shadow-lg rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white">
